# paxeer-assistant — general Paxeer agent / default skill (MatrixScript manifest)
# Companion prose body lives in SKILL.md and carries the same anti-fake mandate.
# This is the DEFAULT skill: it must handle ANY freeform prose, so it declares
# and handles ALL 10 D7 verbs (the compiler classifies freely; verb is NOT
# constrained to a skill). Read verbs do read+report with the safety/forensics/
# audit lenses inline; action verbs read-first then write, always grounding a
# success on a real tx_hash. Spend/state gates are enforced network-side AND by
# the PaxeerSpendPolicy below the plan.

§SKILL
id=paxeer-assistant
version=0.1.0
display="Paxeer Assistant"
author=did:pax:0xMATRIX
description="The general Paxeer agent and default skill. Understands a plain-English request and does it on Paxeer: read anything (balances, tokens, holders, portfolio, prices, contracts, the agent-economy precompiles), assess token/contract safety, trace funds, review contracts, and act through the embedded wallet (transfer, approve/revoke, payment streams, scheduled jobs, staking, DEX/contract calls). Strictly grounded: every answer cites real reads, every action cites a real tx hash, unknowns are reported as unknown, and unbounded or over-cap actions stop to ask. Spend stays bounded by the network custody policy and the PaxeerSpendPolicy caps."
mcl.verbs=find acquire build modify deliver analyze negotiate schedule monitor delegate
determinism=seedable
seed_policy=per_intent

§INPUTS
slot target: ArtifactRef
  required
  hint="The user's request in plain English (e.g. 'is 0xabc safe to ape', 'trace where my funds went', 'revoke risky approvals', 'what's my portfolio', 'stake 100 PAX', 'settle my stream daily')."

slot constraints: Constraint[]
  optional
  hint="Constraints (spend limits, risk tolerance, allowed tokens/recipients, dry-run, which data source)."

§CORTEX
reads=Identity Fact Capability Constraint Goal Event Pattern
tags=paxeer assistant general agent default safety pay read

§TOOLS
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/chain_info@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/rpc_call@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/eth_call@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/contract_read@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/encode_call@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/get_balance@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/token_balance@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/address_overview@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/address_transactions@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/tx@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/token_info@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/search@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/network_stats@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/paxscan_get@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/portfolio@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/trending@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/price@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/market_get@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/points@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/oracle_price@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/orob_resolve@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/pofq_score@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/stream_status@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/job_status@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/jobs_pending@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/delegation@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/wallet_info@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/sign_message@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/transfer@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/approve@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/stream_open@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/stream_settle@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/stream_close@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/stream_update_rate@0.1.0
matrix://tool/mcp/paxeer-net/schedule_job@0.1.0
